<html>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"></meta>
<body style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
#if ($documents.isEmpty())
Your query - <b>&quot;$query&quot;</b> - did not return any documents.<br><br> 

Suggestions:<ul>
<li>Make sure all words are spelled correctly.
<li>Try different keywords.
<li>Try more general keywords.
</ul>
#end
#if ($cluster)
<div style="color: white; font-weight: bold; background-color: #5588BE; border-bottom: 1px solid #303030; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-top: 4px;">
$cluster.Label
</div><br/>
#end
#foreach ($document in $documents)
<a href="$document.getField("url")"><b>$document.getField("title")</b></a>
<span style="color: gray;"> [$document.Id]</span><br>
$document.getField("summary")<br>
<font color=green>$document.getField("url")</font><br><br>
#end
</body></html>